data.description: This fabulously refreshed and conveniently located home is ready for a new family! Upgrades are abundant. Quartz counters, LVP flooring, fresh interior and exterior paint and lots of lighting and plumbing upgrades. Enjoy the privacy of the expansive 2 level back deck that backs up to a wooded area. Other bonuses for you are new roof in 2022, hvac replaced in 2020, and water heater 2021.
